m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: Each time this +3 earth breaker lands a hit, it {g|Encyclopedia:Healing}heals{/g} the wielder by {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d3{/g} and grants 1d6 temporary {g|Encyclopedia:HP}hit points{/g}.

m_DisplayNameText.LocalisedValue: Furious Magic Beast Bane Earth Breaker +1

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +4 giant bane earth breaker grants the wielder a +3 insight {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} to {g|Encyclopedia:Armor_Class}AC{/g} against the undead's {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attacks{/g}.

Whenever this +5 vicious earth breaker lands a hit on an enemy, it applies a stacking -2 {g|Encyclopedia:Armor_Class}AC{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Penalty}penalty{/g} to the target. This penalty disappears once the battle ends.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: An utterance is written on this weapon's handle in the Infernal language: "Let the powerful gain more power. Let the weak grow weaker."

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: Whenever the wielder of this +2 adamantine earth breaker confirms a {g|Encyclopedia:Critical}critical hit{/g} with it, all creatures in a 10-foot range, except for the wielder, have to pass a {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}Reflex saving throw{/g} ({g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} 17) or become prone and unable to stand up for {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d3{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}rounds{/g}.

Whenever this +2 necrotic earth breaker confirms a {g|Encyclopedia:Critical}critical hit{/g} on an enemy, the enemy must pass a {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}Fortitude saving throw{/g} ({g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} 16) or suffer 2 {g|Encyclopedia:Strength}Strength{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:AbilityDamage}ability damage{/g}.

This +3 earth breaker was forged in Abyss and can be wielded only by evil or chaotic creatures. Whenever this weapon lands a hit on an enemy, the enemy must pass a {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}Fortitude saving throw{/g} ({g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} 26) or be consumed in an abyssal flame for {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d4{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}rounds{/g}. This fire deals 1d6 unholy {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g} and 1 damage to {g|Encyclopedia:Strength}Strength{/g} each round. Multiple applications of this effect don't stack.

Whenever this +3 earth breaker confirms a {g|Encyclopedia:Critical}critical hit{/g}, all creatures in a 10-foot range have to pass a {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}Fortitude saving throw{/g} ({g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} 23) or be pushed away for 10 feet and become prone for 1 {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}round{/g}.
This +4 holy earth breaker allows its wielder to cast greater dispel magic at will as a wizard of level equal to the wielder's {g|Encyclopedia:Character_Level}character level{/g}.
This +5 undead bane earth breaker has x4 critical multiplier instead of x3. Its wielder can cast the horrid wilting spell 3 times per day as a 15 level wizard.

Whenever the wielder of this +5 ultrasound earth breaker lands a killing blow, they deal sonic {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g} equal to the number of their ranks in {g|Encyclopedia:Athletics}Athletics{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Skills}skill{/g} to all adjacent enemies. Successful {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}Fortitude save{/g} ({g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} 30) halves the damage.
This is a +1 cold iron ghost touch weapon.

This is a +3 brilliant energy heartseeker weapon. This weapon can tear the soul of a living enemy: whenever it lands a hit, it deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d6{/g} force {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: This weapon was once the seat of Finnean's soul. Now that the soul of the Sarkorian Pathfinder has left the weapon, it has fallen silent forever.
